* Best Practices\nProduction Workloads
** Match Retry Strategy
***_ Network timeout: quick retries
***_ Resource failures: longer intervals
***_ Transient: short intervals (30s-5min)
** Set Reasonable Limits
***_ Max 3 retries recommended
***_ Avoid unlimited retries
***_ Repeated failure = underlying issue
** Monitor Retry Patterns
***_ Gradual increase = infrastructure issues
***_ Track retry frequency over time
** Design for Idempotency
***_ Same result regardless of run count
***_ Makes restarts safe & predictable
** Document Configuration
***_ Why these retry limits?
***_ Why this interval?
***_ Helps future maintainers
@endmindmap
